課程概述 Course Description
       1. Water wave theory – nonlinearity, dispersion and dissipation
2. Boundary layer theory and singular perturbation methods
3. Fluid – structure interaction
4. Fluid and nonlinear dynamics 

課程學習目標 Course Objectives    
	    提供學生有關黏性流場的基本方程式，如何求解，並深入瞭解不同雷諾數下，黏性流場的物理特性。    

課程進度 Course Outline


週次 Week進度說明 Progress Description
1Cartesian tensor analysis and curvilinear coordinates2Fundamental equations of viscous flows3Fundamental equations of viscous flows4Fundamental equations of viscous flows5Exact solutions of Navier-Stokes equations6Exact solutions of Navier-Stokes equations7General properties of Navier-Stokes equations8Low Reynolds-number flows9Low Reynolds-number flows10Midterm exam11Laminar boundary layers12Laminar boundary layers13Stability of laminar flows14Stability of laminar flows15Fundamentals of turbulent flows16Fundamentals of turbulent flows17Turbulent boundary layers18Final exam 

